00:01:10,407 --> 00:01:16,648
bunch of dry stills, but in this case it was very important because we decided early on that we

20
00:01:16,688 --> 00:01:23,310
wanted to pursue a comic book aesthetic. And I'm not someone who really likes half measures,

21
00:01:23,670 --> 00:01:27,371
so when we went for the comic book aesthetic we all bought into the idea of

22
00:01:28,352 --> 00:01:31,735
