00:05:30,904 --> 00:05:36,989
working in the game at this time. And I think you can see here that I was really pushing,

67
00:05:37,489 --> 00:05:42,272
maybe beyond, what was reasonable for how the interface would look like comic book panels.

68
00:05:42,933 --> 00:05:48,297
I wanted to have panels themselves be sort of part interface and part storytelling,

69
00:05:48,317 --> 00:05:49,377
so it was all mixed together.

