00:06:14,490 --> 00:06:18,551
the ui elements to kind of guide you through it but i find it really interesting to look back

75
00:06:18,912 --> 00:06:20,792
back at these with some fondness

76
00:06:21,760 --> 00:06:24,361
And it's interesting that the colours were very different in these as well.

77
00:06:26,181 --> 00:06:30,782
We hadn't come up with the idea of orgs yet, the organisations which are on the different

