00:09:16,111 --> 00:09:21,134
And it's sort of funny to see how quickly I fall back to that when I'm pushed into a

116
00:09:21,174 --> 00:09:21,474
corner.

117
00:09:22,335 --> 00:09:28,079
So I liked all of this stuff and we thought it looked cool, but our main concern was that

118
00:09:28,099 --> 00:09:29,440
it didn't look particularly unique.

119
00:09:30,381 --> 00:09:34,703
at best it would look like good animation, and at worst it would just look like, I don't know,

120
00:09:34,743 --> 00:09:40,265
bad animation. You can see here too the enemy design was really nothing like what we ended up

