00:10:23,826 --> 00:10:26,168
and none of us were really that happy with them.

130
00:10:26,348 --> 00:10:30,250
We knew that we needed some enemies that I could animate reasonably easily.

131
00:10:30,931 --> 00:10:34,433
All of the enemies we already knew were going to be hand animated by myself,

